TITLE: Creating an oRPC Client with Fetch Link in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create an oRPC client using the fetch link implementation. It shows setting up authorization headers and creating clients for both router and contract-based APIs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unnoq/orpc/blob/main/packages/client/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

