TITLE: Implementing Metadata and Caching in oRPC Procedures (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define metadata for oRPC procedures, implement a caching middleware, and use metadata to control caching behavior. It includes the definition of an ORPCMetadata interface, creation of a base handler with middleware, and an example procedure with caching enabled.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unnoq/orpc/blob/main/apps/content/docs/metadata.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
